---
layout: base.njk
title: CodeMint · 编程学习与工程实践
description: 记录编程学习、工程实践和技术复盘，把问题拆开，把经验留下，把认知一点点推进。
---
<main>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner container">
      <div class="hero-copy">
        <p class="eyebrow">Engineering notes · Ship cleanly · Think deeply</p>
        <h1>CodeMint</h1>
        <p class="sub-title">记录编程学习、工程实践和技术复盘，把问题拆开，把经验留下，把认知一点点推进。</p>
        <a href="#latest" class="btn-primary">浏览最新文章</a>
      </div>
      <div class="liquid-device" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="glass-panel panel-main">
          <span class="panel-kicker">~/learning</span>
          <strong>systems · code · notes</strong>
          <code>learn. build. review.</code>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="about" class="container profile-note">
    <h2>About</h2>
    <p class="profile-intro">I write about systems, code, and the engineering notes worth keeping.</p>
    <div class="career-list" aria-label="Experience timeline">
      <div class="career-item">
        <span>2011 - 2015</span>
        <strong>Zhejiang University</strong>
      </div>
      <div class="career-item">
        <span>2015 - 2017</span>
        <strong>TP-LINK</strong>
      </div>
      <div class="career-item">
        <span>2017 - 2018</span>
        <strong>Yunanbao, Qi-Anxin Group</strong>
      </div>
      <div class="career-item">
        <span>2018 - Present</span>
        <strong>Huawei</strong>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="focus-list" aria-label="Technical focus">
      <span>Network Programming</span>
      <span>Distributed Systems</span>
      <span>Cloud Native</span>
      <span>Inference Acceleration</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="latest" class="container">
    <div class="section-title-row">
      <h2>最新文章</h2>
      <div class="tools-row">
        <label class="search-box">
          <span>⌕</span>
          <input id="post-search" type="search" placeholder="搜索文章" autocomplete="off" />
        </label>
        <div class="tag-row" id="tag-filter" role="list" aria-label="标签筛选"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="post-list" class="timeline">
      {% for group in collections.posts | groupByYear %}
        <section class="timeline-year-group" aria-labelledby="year-{{ group.year }}">
          <h3 id="year-{{ group.year }}" class="timeline-year">{{ group.year }}</h3>
          <div class="timeline-year-items">
            {% for post in group.items %}
              <article class="timeline-item post-card" data-title="{{ post.data.title }}" data-excerpt="{{ post.data.description }}" data-tags="{{ post.data.tags | join(' ') }}">
                <time class="timeline-date" datetime="{{ post.date | isoDate }}">{{ post.date | monthDay }}</time>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                  <h3><a href="{{ post.url | url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
                </div>
              </article>
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
        </section>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
